text: Thank you, Mr. Luther for a wonderful assistance in booking my ticket. It was the first experience for me to reserve the air ticket and have a flight with the Swiss Air. The reservation process seemed to take time a little bit in order to proceed things accurately. I very appreciate Mr. Luther's patience and a service mind he had for the customer today.
